track_notes: Walking to the summit by this way is the shortest and easiest path. The are some other track but you must use ropes! When the wx is windy it is better not to go there. In summer time you must have enought water.
track_title: One of the nicest sota in the Marseille area

track_notes: Very nice track for good walker 12km and more than 650m ascent; plus the visit of the Church cave.
